<H1>Setting environment variables: BASH shell</H1>

<P>To change an environment variable use the command:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>VARNAME=<EM>value of variable</EM></STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>By convention, the variable name is given in upper case.</P>

